{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Emmeet wehrâ juhs\nDebbesis / jo es runna-\nſchu/ un laid ta Semme\ndsird mannas Muttes Walloḍu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manna Mahziba laid pill\nka Leetus / un manna Walloḍa\nlaid tekk ka ta Raffa/itt ka fmalks\nLeetus pahr to Sattumu/ un itt\nka tahs Lahfas pahr to Sahli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es gribbu ta KUNGA\nWahrdu isfankt / dohdeet augstn\nGohdu muhſam Deewam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch irr tas Akmira-\nKalns / wiꞥſch Darbs irr bes\nWainas/ jo wiſti wiꞥſch Zetti irr\nTeesa / TAS STIPRAJS\nDEEWS irr Pateefiba/ un ne\nirr Netaifniba/ taiſns un rahms\nirr wiꞥſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee irr faunaitaischees/ wiꞥ-\nnu Waina ne peeklahjabs wiꞥſch\nBehrneem/ ta irr weena nikna un\npahrwehrtita Tauta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Arrig tu ta tam KUN-\nGAM atmaksati / tu trakka un\nneſaprattiga Tauta/neggi wiꞥſch\nirr taws Tehivs/ kas tew atpirzis\nirr / kas tew darrijs un fataifijs\nirr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atminnt to preekſchaju\nMuhschu/ nemmeet wehrâ tohs\nGaddus no Raddu Raddeem/\nwaiza tawn Tehwu / tad wiꞥſch\ntew to stahstihs/ tawns Wezza-\njuē/ tad wiꞥſch tew fazzihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tas Wiſſu-augstakajs\nto Ihpafchunu teem Laudim is-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta KUNGA Datta ir\nwiꞥſch Laudis/ Jehkabs irr wiꞥ-\nna Ihpaſchuuna Mehen-Auklis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch atradde to tuḱ-\nſcha Semmê/ breeſniga Rauf-\nſchanas Tuḱnesi/ un wedde wiꞥ-\nxu apkahrt / wiꞥſch painahzija\nto/ wiꞥſch paſargaja to / itt ka\ntawu Azz-Ranqu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka Ehrglis fatwit Per-\nrekli paſkubbina/ un pahr faueem\nBehrneem liddina : wiꞥſch is-\npleſch farus Spahrnus/ un neut\nwiꞥſus/ un nefis wiꞥſus us fa-\nueem Spahrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGGS ween wad-\ndija tohs/ un fiveſch Deews ar\nwiꞥſu newa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch eezeble to pahr\ntabm augstahm Semmes Wee-\ntahm/ ka wiꞥſch ehde ta Tibru-\nma Auglus/ un likke Meddu no\nAkmira-Kalna fiſst / un Etji no\nzeeta Akmira.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sweestu no Gohwim/\nun Peenu no Awin / ar teem\nTaufeem no Jehreem/ un taukus\nAunus un Ahſchus ar taukahm\nIhkstim / Kweefchn-Grandeem /\nun to Ohgu Sulln / fchkiſstu\nWiḥnu effi tu dsehris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu *Jeschurun tauks\ntappe/ tad spehre wiꞥſch/ tu effi\ntauks tappis/ un refns/ un Tau-\nka fajehmees/ tad atstabje wiꞥſch\nDeewu fawu Darritaju/ un niẓ-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
